<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0" xml:id="zend.application.available-resources.layout"><info><title>Zend_Application_Resource_Layout</title></info>
    

    <para>
        <classname>Zend_Application_Resource_Layout</classname> peut être utilisé pour configurer
        <classname>Zend_Layout</classname>. Les options de configurations sont les mêmes que
        celles de <link linkend="zend.layout.options"><classname>Zend_Layout</classname></link>.
    </para>

    <example xml:id="zend.application.available-resources.layout.configExample"><info><title>Exemple de configuration de layout</title></info>
        

        <para>
            Ci-dessous un exemple de code <acronym>INI</acronym> montrant comment configurer
            la ressource layout.
        </para>

        <programlisting language="ini"><![CDATA[
resources.layout.layout = "NomDuLayoutParDefaut"
resources.layout.layoutPath = "/chemin/vers/layouts"
]]></programlisting>
    </example>
</section>
